* CRUD
** the 7 crud routes.
** GET
   Path                     |route
   -------------------------+---------
    - /<resource>           |index  
    - /<resource>/new       |new
    - /<resource>/:id/edit  |edit
    - /<resource>/:id       |show
** POST
    - /<resource>/:id       |update
    - /<resource>           |create
    - /<resource>/:id/remove|delete
